DO use structured interviews, standardized assessments, self-report measurements, and evidence-based treatments throughout therapy. Scientifically supported assessments and therapies have shown high success rates (Norcross & Wampold,
         2011
      ). A description of evidence-based therapies for DSM-5 disorders can be found on the American Psychological Association’s Division 12 (Society of Clinical Psychology) website.
